04:32.883 --> 04:40.875
qualified military personnel.

04:42.939 --> 04:45.442
So the relationship was very, very good. One thing 
that I was wondering about is that, well, they just

04:47.205 --> 04:59.464
retired Admiral Rickover, and I was wondering if 
you worked on the submarine project and the

04:47.205 --> 04:59.464
development of the nuclear subs. Even though, of 
course, this is Air Force versus Navy, but still.

05:03.803 --> 05:10.831
