05:53.258 --> 06:11.106
I took over the general manager of the commission, 
of course, he was head of the nuclear submarine

05:53.258 --> 06:11.106
division of the reactor development division of 
the staff. And so in that capacity was under the

06:11.606 --> 06:18.557
general manager. And so he submitted his programs 
to me and budgets, and they were all blended into

06:18.773 --> 06:36.511
the reactor development budget and the 
commission budget and defended before the

06:18.773 --> 06:36.511
Congress and wherever. And of course, Rickover 
was quite good before the Congress in his own

06:37.332 --> 06:46.722
defense, but it takes more than Rickover to get his 
money. So for the six years that I was there, I

06:47.056 --> 06:56.425
defended his budget before the Congress, as did 
he.

07:01.809 --> 07:05.092
So I was fairly deeply involved. I've got a whole 
bunch of pictures in there of the launching of one

07:06.113 --> 07:15.662
of the subs in which I participated.

