Rickover has his friends and his critics in 
Congress, and he's just been in forced

07:20.030 --> 07:26.137
retirement. It's been said that he was very 
difficult to get along with, especially if you

07:26.898 --> 07:33.745
were on the wrong side of him. What was your 
relationship like? What type of person did you

07:36.588 --> 07:38.210
think he was? Well, I think there's no such thing as 
getting along with Rickover, for anybody, not for

07:40.232 --> 07:47.901
me or for anybody else. The question is... just how 
badly do you get tangled up with him, and can you go

07:49.308 --> 08:00.743
ahead and accomplish what both of you are trying to 
accomplish in spite of that fact? And I think I was

08:02.325 --> 08:04.788
able to do that.

08:10.316 --> 08:14.782
So I think if Rick and I were talking, we'd say the 
same things about each other. I'd have a little

08:14.802 --> 08:17.425
different emphasis than he does. And

08:18.265 --> 08:28.859
I have a great deal of respect for his abilities and 
capabilities in a number of areas. And in some

08:28.879 --> 08:30.621
other areas, I think he's nuts. I suspect he'd say 
the same thing about me. In spite of the fact that he

08:44.793 --> 08:56.169
is very, very good and has done a wonderful job, I 
think, overall for the nation in creating a

08:44.793 --> 08:56.169
nuclear subsurface navy. And I think he has done 
that.

09:02.037 --> 09:08.826
I think he's done a lot of damage to particular to 
other aspects of the armed forces. For example?

09:10.169 --> 09:13.434
For the surface Navy is one example. I'm sure the 
Secretary of the Navy or the Black Shoe Admirals

09:13.715 --> 09:25.534
are not a damn bit happy about a lot of the things 
he's doing. I'm sure of

09:25.554 --> 09:30.422
it. He has pressed the contractors, Rick has, the 
electric boat, the other people who do the work,

09:35.975 --> 09:48.430
but more particularly their subcontractor,

09:35.975 --> 09:48.430
to the point that it's just almost impossible to 
work with them. Well, you can't condemn all of

