09:50.273 --> 10:00.345
by with. But it's not all of them, all of the time.

10:08.844 --> 10:13.871
There has to be an accommodation so you can get on 
with your job. But his is a fight from daylight till

10:15.934 --> 10:25.849
dark with any contractor that he's working with.

10:26.030 --> 10:30.957
Most of the naval officers that work with him, 
manning the submarines, just, just

10:31.696 --> 10:37.662
can hardly stomach it at all.

